<manpage>
    <volume> 常用数据结构 </volume>
    <class>U8StringBuf</class>
    <method> LastIndexOf </method>

    <description>
        <para> 按UTF-8编码格式报告指定的U8String在此对象中的最后一个匹配项的索引位置。</para>
    </description>
    <syntax>
        <return_val> Int32 </return_val>
        <modifier>const</modifier>
        <parameters>
        <api_param>
            <param_type>const U8String &amp; </param_type>
            <param_name> str </param_name>
            <param_note>
                <para> 子串 </para>
            </param_note>
        </api_param>
        <api_param>
            <param_type>StringCase</param_type>
            <param_name> stringCase  </param_name>
            <param_default> StringCase_Sensitive</param_default>
            <param_note>
                <para> 是否区分大小写标志。参见<link url="../../others/StringCase.htm">StringCase</link>枚举类型说明。</para>
            </param_note>
        </api_param>  
        
        </parameters>        
    </syntax>
    <return>
        <para>返回str在U8StringBuf对象字符串中最后出现的索引值；如果没有出现，则返回-1。</para>
    </return>
     <remarks>
        <para>若StringBuf对象字符串指针为NULL或字符串内容为空，或str指针为NULL，则返回-1。</para>
        <para>若指定字符串不在U8StringBuf对象字符串中或U8StringBuf对象字符串为空，则返回-1。</para>
        <para>若str内容为空串，则返回源串的最后一个字符的索引值。</para>
    </remarks>
<example>
<pre>
U8StringBuf_&lt;20&gt; u8sbuf;   
u8sbuf.Copy("abcabc");
U8String u8s1 = "bc";
U8String u8s2 = "bd";
CConsole::WriteLine(u8sbuf.LastIndexOf(u8s1));  //Display : 4
CConsole::WriteLine(u8sbuf.LastIndexOf(au8s2));  //Display : -1
</pre>
</example>
<references>
    <reference>
        <ref_name>U8StringBuf::LastIndexOf</ref_name>
        <ref_url>LastIndexOf</ref_url>
    </reference>
</references>   
</manpage>